<h1>Fleet Intake Form</h1>
<p class="lead">Submit your fleet details for a custom wrap quote. Tell us your vehicle types, quantities, and timeline. The team responds within 2 business hours with vehicle-specific pricing — not a range, a number.</p>
<div class="trust"><span>⚡ <strong>2-Hour</strong> Response</span><span>🚐 <strong>Free</strong> Fleet Pickup</span><span>✅ <strong>Avery Dennison &amp; 3M</strong> Certified</span><span>📍 <strong>Chicago, IL</strong></span></div>
<h2>What We Need From You</h2>
<ul style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);padding-left:20px;line-height:2.2">
<li><strong>Vehicle types</strong> — Year, make, model (e.g. 2024 Ford Transit High Roof)</li>
<li><strong>Vehicle count</strong> — How many vehicles need wrapping</li>
<li><strong>Wrap type</strong> — Full wrap, partial wrap, color change, or spot graphics</li>
<li><strong>Artwork</strong> — Existing logos/artwork or need design from scratch</li>
<li><strong>Timeline</strong> — When do you need the vehicles wrapped</li>
<li><strong>Pickup location</strong> — Where are the vehicles located</li>
</ul>
<h2>How It Works</h2>
<ul style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);padding-left:20px;line-height:2.2">
<li><strong>Step 1:</strong> Submit your fleet details via the estimate form or call (312) 597-1286</li>
<li><strong>Step 2:</strong> Receive vehicle-specific pricing within 2 business hours</li>
<li><strong>Step 3:</strong> Approve design on exact vehicle templates</li>
<li><strong>Step 4:</strong> Free pickup from your location — we come to you</li>
<li><strong>Step 5:</strong> Installation at our climate-controlled Chicago facility</li>
<li><strong>Step 6:</strong> Delivery back to your location, wrapped and inspected</li>
</ul>
